"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.2.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.2.6</span> 标题：嚼环和辔头（bit and bridle）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מֶתֶג</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：metheg)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:28\">2KI 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:3\">PRO 26:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:29\">ISA 37:29</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：רֶסֶן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：resen)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:5\">JOB 41:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:28\">ISA 30:28</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：χαλινός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chalinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:3\">JAS 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:20\">REV 14:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：χρυσοχάλινος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chrusochalinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:29\">2MA 10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd3:6\">1ES 3:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κόσμος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kosmos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc5:3\">2MA 5:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σαγή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：sagē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc3:25\">2MA 3:25</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0009_bronze_horse_bit.jpg\" alt=\"古代青铜马衔\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">古代青铜马衔 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>嚼环是一根短棍，通常由金属制成，放在马的嘴里。短棍的两端从马嘴的两侧突出来，系上绳索或皮带，这些绳索或皮带套在马的头部就成为辔头。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0969_harness_bridle_hans.jpg\" alt=\"辔头和嚼环\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">辔头和嚼环 (© Gary Todd - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>骑马者或车夫可以通过拉扯辔头左侧或右侧的带子来控制马的行动。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0932_horse.jpg\" alt=\"马和骑手展示缰绳的使用\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">马和骑手展示缰绳的使用 (© Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>希伯来文<em>metheg</em> 和<em>resen</em> 分别指“嚼环”和“辔头”（虽然<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:3\">PRO 26:3</a> 将<em>metheg</em> 译为“bridle”“辔头”）。希腊文<em>chalinos</em> 和<em>chrusochalinos</em> 既指嚼环也指辔头。如果嚼环和辔头等挽具在当地不为人所知，翻译者可以使用描述性的短语，例如“引导马匹的某物”或“放入马嘴里面以引导它的某物”。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:20\">ZEC 14:20</a> 中，希伯来文<em>mtsilah</em> 可能是指马的挽具上面会发出某种响声的装饰。在圣经中，这个词只出现在这里。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:20\">REV 14:20</a> 提到“马的辔头”（“a horse’s bridle”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）仅仅是用来指高度，即辔头离地面的高度，因此我们可以将这个高度译为“约一米半高”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> ）或“约五英尺高”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:29\">2MA 10:29</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd3:6\">1ES 3:6</a> 所用的希腊文词语表明，辔头的金属件是由金子制成的。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
